    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Once the chicken has slightly browned, transfer it to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray (reserve the pan!) and put in the oven for 17-18 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>coconut chicken</strong></p>",
